Gluster Build process

* STEP 1 - Toolchain Setup
bash# wget ftp://ftp.zresearch.com/pub/gluster/release/current/gluster-toolchain-i686.tar.gz 
bash# tar -C /usr/local -xjf gluster-toolchain-$(ARCH).tar.bz2


* STEP 2 - PATH setup

bash# export PATH=$PATH:/usr/local/gluster-toolchain/bin

* STEP 3 - Configure

bash# ./configure --host=i686-gluster-linux-gnu --build=i686-pc-linux-gnu --prefix=/usr 

Both --host= and --build= are mandatory

* STEP 3 - Build and Burn

bash# make iso
...
bash# cdrecord -data gluster-<version-<arch>.iso

